{
  "stem": "6719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, what do they say here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have an expression here, uh, that a guy says, uh, uh, he's a cardiac Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, in his heart he's a Jew, but he doesn't do anything else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, you know, if-- I'm not putting myself into-- into the-- into-- into this group, as such, but-- but I was too young.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, today, as you know, and as everybody else knows, uh, kids have a chance for a Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure that there-- there must have been something down there too at that time, and maybe there was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How do you feel about your Jewishness now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, uh, maybe even stronger than ever because if you-- if-- if you burn yourself, or if you get a traffic ticket, you remember when and how you burned yourself, and you remember where you got your traffic ticket.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I remember that what I saw, that happened-- and I never use the expression what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It happened to all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, if that doesn't teach, or taught, me a lesson, then what the hell will?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Simple as that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother-in-law got me in there about, what, 25, 30 years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Habonim, the builders.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only go there twice a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It used to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, as-- as a matter of fact, it wasn't-- it wasn't survivors that started that synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was, uh, immigrants that started it that came here either during the war from Portugal-- there were-- you know, there were people that came during the war from Portugal.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of them were Germans and Austrians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, uh, it-- it blossomed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
